      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit exhibits a robust power band with the Double VANOS system functioning within factory tolerances and individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate common floor pan fatigue, while the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a tight limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains within spec. While the exterior shows honest patina, the drivetrain and kinematics are primed for spirited use.",
